					<p>Wikipedia <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramen">describes ramen</a> as:</p>
					<blockquote>a Japanese noodle dish [that] consists of Chinese-style wheat noodles served in a meat- or fish-based broth.</blockquote>
